data.meta_description: A global leader in factual television, we have produced amazing shows with our partners around the world for over 20 years. We are a team of professionals who are passionate about the development, production, co-production and financing of factual and scripted content. A sister company of Thunderbird Entertainment, our work is seen in more than 170 countries.
data.text: Our programs are seen in more than 170 countries worldwide. Founded in 2010, Great Pacific Media specializes in development, production, co-production, and financing of factual, lifestyle, documentary, and reality television. In 2016 GPM was acquired by the Thunderbird Group of Companies to accelerate the growth of Thunderbirds presence in the unscripted television space.
